The Sunken Sanctum is an ancient ruin buried beneath a collapsed mountain.

Those who delve within will face the remnants of their experiments -- creatures

twisted by centuries of uncontrolled magic.  Deep within the Sanctum lie hidden

chambers sealed by ancient puzzles.  Those who solve them may discover paths to

even more dangerous areas.  Recommended level: 150-170.

